column3: Verification of vowel phonemes by Linguist

column230: in the first instance of tIM, speaker 109 seems to hv pronounced tI, In mhaje aavayk saang also, the pronunciation of e is difficult to identify bcz of the following diphthong A in aavayk. Also for mhajEM pustak kEnnA haDUn ditlO example, the EM in mhajEM is not very prominently heard.
